/-!
# Preferred physical scalar Program P-B closure

This is the recommended aggregate head for the scalar physical branch.

The preferred endpoint has removed the following independent inputs:

* physical-measure full support;
* periodic and antiperiodic boundary-core density;
* an independently supplied tangential Green density;
* the time-period integral cancellation, when a periodic primitive is used;
* a field-dependent normal integral identity, when the universal half-collar
  transport is used;
* normal trace regularity and its constants;
* maximal-adjoint regularity and smooth adjoint approximation;
* an arbitrary bounded zeroth-order energy operator;
* pointwise coefficient functions and their six `MemLp` proofs;
* six coefficient constants and residual-square integrability;
* an endomorphism-valued positive square;
* finite-dimensionality proofs for the ranges of Rellich approximants.

The smallest current complete data package uses:

1. an intrinsic global scalar-wave representative;
2. one normal Green component.  It may be supplied directly, decomposed through
   a periodic time primitive, or generated by a field-independent transport to
   the positive half collar;
3. a scalar first-jet energy remainder;
4. six continuous operators from the completed Cauchy boundary to boundary
   `L²`, together with the exact canonical residual expansion;
5. a closed Lagrangian condition;
6. an external positive-square decomposition of one real shifted form;
7. finite-coordinate factorizations converging to `H¹ -> L²`.

The preferred completed-boundary endpoint is
`P0EFTJanusMappingTorusCanonicalPhysicalScalarIntrinsicWaveCanonicalNormalRieszScalarEnergyL2OperatorPDEClosure4D`.
The preferred complete endpoint is
`P0EFTJanusMappingTorusCanonicalPhysicalScalarIntrinsicWaveCanonicalNormalRieszScalarEnergyL2OperatorMinimalProgramPClosure4D`.
The complete frontier is flattened by
`P0EFTJanusMappingTorusCanonicalPhysicalScalarProgramPFinalObligations4D`.
The two most local Green implementation paths are
`P0EFTJanusMappingTorusCanonicalPhysicalScalarIntrinsicWaveTangentialTimePrimitiveFinalClosure4D`
and
`P0EFTJanusMappingTorusCanonicalPhysicalScalarIntrinsicWaveTransportedNormalFinalClosure4D`.
All three paths expose Dirichlet, Neumann and constant Robin specializations.
-/

namespace JanusFormal
namespace P0EFTJanusMappingTorusCanonicalPhysicalScalarProgramPBPreferredClosure4D

set_option autoImplicit false
noncomputable section

/-- Marker for the preferred completed-boundary endpoint. -/
theorem canonicalPhysicalScalarProgramPBPreferredPDEClosure_available : True :=
  trivial

/-- Marker for the flattened final obligations package. -/
theorem canonicalPhysicalScalarProgramPBFinalObligations_available : True :=
  P0EFTJanusMappingTorusCanonicalPhysicalScalarProgramPFinalObligations4D.canonicalPhysicalScalarProgramPFinalObligations_available

/-- Marker for the preferred smallest complete scalar Program P-B endpoint. -/
theorem canonicalPhysicalScalarProgramPBPreferredClosure_available : True :=
  P0EFTJanusMappingTorusCanonicalPhysicalScalarIntrinsicWaveCanonicalNormalRieszScalarEnergyL2OperatorMinimalProgramPClosure4D.canonicalPhysicalScalarIntrinsicWaveCanonicalNormalRieszScalarEnergyL2OperatorMinimalProgramPClosure_available

/-- Marker for the periodic-time-primitive final endpoint. -/
theorem canonicalPhysicalScalarProgramPBTimePrimitiveClosure_available : True :=
  P0EFTJanusMappingTorusCanonicalPhysicalScalarIntrinsicWaveTangentialTimePrimitiveFinalClosure4D.canonicalPhysicalScalarIntrinsicWaveTangentialTimePrimitiveFinalClosure_available

/-- Marker for the universal-transport final endpoint. -/
theorem canonicalPhysicalScalarProgramPBTransportedNormalClosure_available : True :=
  P0EFTJanusMappingTorusCanonicalPhysicalScalarIntrinsicWaveTransportedNormalFinalClosure4D.canonicalPhysicalScalarIntrinsicWaveTransportedNormalFinalClosure_available

/-- Marker for the preferred standard boundary families. -/
theorem canonicalPhysicalScalarProgramPBPreferredStandardBoundaries_available : True :=
  P0EFTJanusMappingTorusCanonicalPhysicalScalarIntrinsicWaveCanonicalNormalRieszScalarEnergyL2OperatorStandardBoundaryProgramPClosure4D.canonicalPhysicalScalarIntrinsicWaveCanonicalNormalRieszScalarEnergyL2OperatorStandardBoundaryProgramPClosure_available

end
end P0EFTJanusMappingTorusCanonicalPhysicalScalarProgramPBPreferredClosure4D
